<p>Interested? <%= mail_to("hello@openlectures.org", "Let's talk!", :encode => "javascript") %>. We'll work things out for you.</p>
<h3 class="marginbot0">Paradise</h3>
<p>Every weekend at openlectures is full of surprises. It's a large happy family who'll willingly try a thousand things to get one lecture done right. <span class="salmon">When you join us, you join our family.</span></p>
